data.description: Needs nothing other than to move in! Custom built, Unique, Immaculately kept, modern renovated, 3,770 sft house.  This property is being sold "as is," and underwent a complete gut and remodel of all floors in 2016 with the following scope of work: Custom built in 2004 and renovated in 2016 with high end finishes. - Full finish basement - New mechanicals throughout the house - High end finishes, high end ceilings, in ceiling speakers - Master Suite w/ walk in closets - 15 Rooms in total w/ Large Pantry and Office and lots of storage space - Fully finished basement with access to garage - Custom kitchen w/ built in pantry and appliances - Drive through garage - Backyard with natural gas lines and terracotta canopy
